From: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jul 2024 23:38:10 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 59/78] Platform/Sgi: Include HobPrintLib

Due to a recent change, Standalone MM module needs an additional lib to
print the HOB information at the start of StandaloneMmMain().

Include the lib to fix the build.

Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
---
 Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatformMm.dsc.inc | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatformMm.dsc.inc b/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatformMm.dsc.inc
index b34b5fcd63d3..203e34b4d5fb 100644
--- a/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatformMm.dsc.inc
+++ b/Platform/ARM/SgiPkg/SgiPlatformMm.dsc.inc
@@ -50,6 +50,7 @@
   PL011UartLib|ArmPlatformPkg/Library/PL011UartLib/PL011UartLib.inf
   SerialPortLib|ArmPlatformPkg/Library/PL011SerialPortLib/PL011SerialPortLib.inf
 !endif
+  HobPrintLib|MdeModulePkg/Library/HobPrintLib/HobPrintLib.inf
 
   #
   # Entry point
